{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/HadThisDream.png?t=1732324018\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up in a strange place, the air is heavy and dense. Tall green walls surround you, a purple sky... no, purple mist hangs above you. In the distance a clock chimes, maybe a voice calling out to you. Something moves in the fog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this puzzle-adventure horror game you must solve puzzles and find special items to escape in one of four ways in a dreamscape-like maze. A playful and malicious creature stalks through the hedges, hearing and seeing everything. It moves quick, stay out of its way and sightline. Find useful items to navigate the maze and unlock areas, or fighting the creature. Manage your limited items and defenses to keep yourself alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/Passing_Through.gif?t=1732324018\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/TheNightmare.png?t=1732324018\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A giant hedge maze with interactables scattered around, the layout of the maze is unchanging but items and puzzles are slightly randomized. Every piece has its puzzle, every item you find is useful. There is a threat, the forest goes silent when a predator is around. Don't let it hear or see you, it is unlikely you will escape. Use noise and sound to your advantage, you'll hear it before it can hear you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Locate items to scare it away, even if for a moment. Ration your defenses, each item can used in multiple ways and some defense items are required for puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/Door_Open.gif?t=1732324018\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/ExtraInfo.png?t=1732324018\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controls are explained in the options menu, everything else is exploratory or hinted through voicelines and color coding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collectables can be found in the main menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only specific events and triggers will auto save progress, manual saving requires a specific item and interactable in the map. Average playtime is 2 to 3 hours, this will likely change person to person based on navigational and memorization ability. Total completion will likely come out to 5 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If the game opens on the wrong monitor turn off fullscreen and move the application window to the correct screen, then reenable fullscreen. Credits are unlocked after completing at least one playthrough; there are four &quot;endings&quot; which are shown in the main menu. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/Fight_Tryian.gif?t=1732324018\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240970/extras/Disclaimer.png?t=1732324018\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are not responsible for any supernatural activity or dreams you experience in relation to Entity 15.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just a dream?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3240970/e3d3b23e18e48102b7d25afa96c21b9e3a6db8cc.jpg"},{"name":"Tick 